sentences.english: The series equipment is used in production of polyester bottle-packing carbonate drink.

sentences.english: So it is feasible to discriminate gas-bearing reservoir by using prestack simultaneous inversion technique.
sentences.chinese: 因而，应用同步反演技术进行含气储层识别是可行的。

sentences.english: The result shows that the method is effective in gas-bearing reservoir prediction.
sentences.chinese: 结果表明该方法进行含气储层预测是有效的。

sentences.english: Seismic response in heterogeneous gas-bearing strata would be characterized by relatively well developed diffracted wave.
sentences.chinese: 非均质性含气地层其波场响应中绕射波比较发育。

sentences.english: Porosity and gas-saturation are two important parameters in quantitive reservoir interpretation.
sentences.chinese: 孔隙度和含气饱和度是气层定量解释的两个重要参数。

sentences.english: It is difficult to differentiate gas-bearing sand from dense sand in lithologic interpretation.
sentences.chinese: 在岩性解释上，很难区分含气砂岩和致密砂岩。

sentences.english: The utility model relates to a metal container filled with gas-containing liquid.
sentences.chinese: 一种含气液体灌装金属容器。

sentences.english: There are indications of gas sands on record section.
sentences.chinese: 在记录剖面上有含气砂岩迹象。

sentences.english: Hence , people should pay more attention to the research on the lower of the valve.
sentences.chinese: 因此，对阀下侧的含气水锤的研究应引起人们的重视。

sentences.english: The gas saturation is one of the petrophysical parameters that are most difficult to obtain.
sentences.chinese: 含气饱和度是最难求解的岩石物理参数之一。

sentences.english: Gas-bearing series of Gangxi Developing Area is Minghuazhen and Guantao Group of upper Tertiary.
